::Firearm::

Firearm smiles, seeing that this bot had her head on straight (not wanting to 
be killed).

"I'm Firearm, nice to meet you," he says in a cheery tone, noticing that she 
was looking at his arm cannon, "That's kinda unremovable. Don't worry, 
though, I won't use it."

He grins at her, "Unless you give me a reason to."
